<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Doações Book</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #d8bb8f;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 60px auto;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .welcome,
        .options-panel {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #000;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 4px 8px 20px 5px rgb(96, 69, 36);
            padding: 28px;
        }

        .welcome {
            text-align: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #743513;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            color: #6b4b2d;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .options {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 16px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .card {
            width: 240px;
            padding: 24px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 2px 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .card.admin {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b571c, #743513);
        }

        .card.user {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b47a3b, #8f5a21);
            cursor: default;
        }

        .card h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .card p {
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .footer-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 24px;
            color: #743513;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="welcome">
            <h1>Bem-vindo ao Doações Book</h1>
            <p>Escolha como deseja acessar o sistema.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="options-panel">
            <div class="options">
                <a class="card admin" href="/admin">
                    <h2>Administrador</h2>
                    <p>Acesse o painel de administração.</p>
                </a>

                <div class="card user">
                    <h2>Usuário</h2>
                    <p>Em breve.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>